    body:
        if has_soap_nearby(sink):
            observe(sink, "Check if soap is used on the underwear")
            wash(underwear)

    # Determine whether there is soap adjacent to the sink
    symbol soap_nearby=exists soap:item: is_soap(soap) and close(soap, sink)
    return soap_nearby

behavior apply_soap(underwear:item, sink:item):

        # Ensure that the underwear is inside the sink
